name: Baa Baa Black Sheep
content: Baa baa black sheep have you any wool
Yes sir yes sir three bags full
黑绵羊咩咩叫,你有没有羊毛
One for the master one for the dame
有有有,先生,我有整整三袋羊毛
一袋送给男主人,一袋送给女主人
